.course-card
    .course-card__card-media
        a.card-media__card-img(href='course_detail_view.html')
            img(src='../assets/images/courses/img-1.jpg' alt='')
            .card-img__card-overlay
                .card-overlay__badge-seller Bestseller
                .card-overlay__crd-reviews
                    i.uil.uil-star
                      | 4.5
                span.card-overlay--play_btn1
                    i.uil.uil-play
                .card-overlay--crd-timer
                    | 25 hours    
    .course-card__card-content
        .card-content__eps_dots--more_dropdown
            a(href='#')
                i.uil.uil-ellipsis-v
            .eps_dots__dropdown-content
                span
                    i.uil.uil-share-alt
                        | Share
                span
                    i.uil.uil-heart
                        | Save
                span
                    i.uil.uil-ban
                        | Not Interested
                span
                    i.uil.uil-windsock
                        | Report
        .card-content__card-details
            span.card-details__card-view 109k views
            span.card-details__card-view 15 days ago
        a.card-content__card-discription(href='course_detail_view.html')
            | Complete Python Bootcamp: Go from zero to hero
            | in Python 3
        a.card-content__card-title(href='#') Web Development | Python
        .card-content__card-auther
            p.card-auther__name-auth
                | By
                a(href='#') John Doe
            .card-auther__price $10
            button.shrt-cart-btn(title='cart')
                i.uil--uil-shopping-cart-alt 